# Exception: the airport_context package's source data dir (airline telephony +
# spoken-name override dictionaries) is tracked source, NOT regenerable data.
# Only the top-level data/ (airport SQLite DB + OurAirports CSV cache) stays ignored.
!python-legacy/airport_context/data/
!python-legacy/airport_context/data/**

# Local-only files — NOT published to GitHub (present on the maintainer's machine).
# NOTE: "local-only" is a PUBLISHING choice, not a purpose label. This list mixes
# PRODUCTION pipeline code with TRAINING tooling — do not assume everything here is
# "training". See the "Maintainer notes" section of python-legacy/README.md.
#
# Production (live inference / proof-of-life), kept local:
main.py
realtime_transcribe.py
live_atc_transcribe.py
